collection.name: ENS: Ethereum Name Service
collection.description: Ethereum Name Service (ENS) domains are secure domain names for the decentralized world. ENS domains provide a way for users to map human readable names to blockchain and non-blockchain resources, like Ethereum addresses, IPFS hashes, or website URLs. ENS domains can be bought and sold on secondary markets.

Crypto Bull Society
collection.description:
The Crypto Bull Society is a group of like-minded individuals who are bullish on the future of crypto. 

Our mission is to increase the GDP of Web 3.0, while trolling the hell out of each other.

Membership is represented by holding a Crypto Bull or Crypto Bear NFT, from our unique private art collection.

Every holder of a Crypto Bull @ 8 February was entitled to claim a Crypto Bear for free.

Check out the Crypto Bear NFT collection: https://opensea.io/collection/crypto-bears-by-cbs

detail.description: The Crypto Bulls are a collection of 7.777 unique ultra-realistic 3D hand-drawn art pieces.
